--- In Read_Alphabet@yahoogroups.com, "satnordameriko"
<satnordameriko@y...> wrote:
> differences. thanks for answering.

The link (www.shawalphabet.com) you are referring to does not contain
the same alphabet as Quikscript. It is a heavily-modified version of
Shavian. Your best bet on having this question completely answered
would be to ask the author of that website of the differences.
